casebody.data:
No. 542. Western Union Telegraph Company v. George M. Brown, Executor, etc., et al. October 28, 1918. Mr. *553Rush Taggart and Mr. Beverly L. Hodghead for petitioner. Mr. William J. Hunsaker and Mr. E. W. Britt for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the Circuit Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted.
